Q: 2024年247 Aviation Ltd在Europe地区的每月总飞行量是多少？提供环比变化。
SQL:
WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                count(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
        WHERE
                a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
                AND b.supplier_id = "1002"
                AND a.dep_area_name = "Europe"
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( SELECT *, lag( num ) over ( ORDER BY date_month ) AS last_num FROM biao_1 ) SELECT
        date_month,
        num,
        concat( round(( num - last_num )/ last_num * 100, 2 ), '%' ) AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
WHERE
        last_num IS NOT NULL;

WITH biao_1 AS (
        SELECT
                a.date_month,
                count(*) AS num
        FROM
                zts_plane_flight_1 a
                JOIN aircraft_details b ON a.pure_reg = b.pure_reg
        WHERE
                a.date_month BETWEEN '2024-01'
                AND '2024-12'
                AND b.supplier_id = "1014"
                AND a.dep_area_name = "Africa"
        GROUP BY
                a.date_month
        ),
        biao_2 AS ( SELECT *, lag( num ) over ( ORDER BY date_month ) AS last_num FROM biao_1 ) SELECT
        date_month,
        num,
        concat( round(( num - last_num )/ last_num * 100, 2 ), '%' ) AS rate
FROM
        biao_2
WHERE
        last_num IS NOT NULL;
